rows.label: qst200802_msg0001
rows.name:
What's with these guys?!
They're just women and kids,
but they're so strong...

rows.label: qst200802_msg0002
rows.name:
You little brats, you'll regret
this! We won't let this go!

rows.label: qst200802_msg0003
rows.name:
Ahh... Such a sore
loser's parting words...

rows.label: qst200802_msg0004
rows.name:
Hey, Hotaru, are you really sure
you don't know those mercenaries?

rows.label: qst200802_msg0005
rows.name:
Yeah, really. I have no
memory of them at all.

rows.label: qst200802_msg0006
rows.name:
Hotaru often receives
presents from people, mo.
Maybe it's about that, mo?

rows.label: qst200802_msg0007
rows.name:
Eh? I don't remember receiving
anything like classified
documents, though...
